OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStorm Dave will clear northeast
OL,6,Fon Sunday morning, leaving sunshine
OL,7,Fand widespread showers across the UK.
OL,8,FNorthern areas will see the heaviest,
OL,9,Fblustery showers and feel cold, while
OL,10,Ftemperatures elsewhere stay closer to
OL,11,Faverage for early April.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers becoming confined to
OL,14,Fthe north and west, with most places
OL,15,Fturning dry with clear spells. A
OL,16,Fchilly night with a fairly widespread
OL,17,Ffrost. Clouding over from the west
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
