OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA chilly start, but mostly dry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud will continue
OL,7,Fto increase across western areas
OL,8,Fthrough the day, with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain reaching the far northwest later.
